snippet.title: Of Kings And Men, Combat trailer
snippet.description:
Early access available on steam, August 25th. 


Of Kings And Men allows you to experience huge, player-driven battles like no other. Engage in massive skirmishes with more than 200 players and practice your fighting skills in competitive matches with an intuitive combat system.

Coming to Early Access in August 2016

Visit http://ofkingsandmen.net/ for more information
